Hyper-sexuality & ADHD can really relate but the unfortunate part is when we feel the pressure to perform on a more “distracted” day so here is some things that can help you cross that finish line with a big smile on your face😉😈 #adhd #adhdafterdark #adhdbrain #adhdexplained #adhdmemes #kinkymemes #kinkcommunity #adhdtips

WHITEFLAG EVENT Tuesday July 11th!

I didn’t expect this to be my favourite live event I have ever done but my GOODNESS that was incredible!!!

We love you guys❤️
#adhd #mentalhealthmatters #neurodivergent #mentalhealthawareness
Need someone to talk to? #mentalhealth #mentalhealthmatters #mentalhealthsupport #whiteflag
@brave.dave.official and I try 6 different flavours of Soda we found in a store and we thought we’d share it with Y’all😂
ADHD truth that I hope y’all understand❤️ #adhd #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdtips

THERE IS A REASON YOU FEEL MORE IMPULSIVE and it’s fine….but there is a reason so don’t forget to remind yourself that you aren’t just “Broken” the strength in your brain is just in other areas❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #adhdsupport

HELPFUL FOOD FOR ADHD IS A STYLE AND NOT A TYPE!! Of course we can always be healthier but especially when you’re starting off please don’t ever forget that you can start SIMPLE you gorgeous creature!❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdbrain #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdtips

Overthinking and the ADHD brain go hand in hand which is WHY we gotta understand that giving ourselves tons to think about before bed time might not be the option!  While absolutely 0 thinking works the best I don’t know about y’all but I’m not there yet so just remember to do things with “less” then you are use to!  It can really help you find another level of calm!  #adhd #adhdbrain #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdtips

I AM SO PUMPED!!!

Longgggggg time coming but I am SO excited to show the first lines of my new Merch!

Everything from Posters, Water Bottles, Totes, Magnets, T-shirts and MORE!

If you ever have a favourite quote of mine that you would love in any format PLEASE let me know!  The response y’all have to my weird way of describing things always has me so happy and I have been working on these lines for a long time!

With colours for every kind of mood/passion I’m so excited to finally show people🥹

Please let me know what you think!  I only want to work on these more to really give you something awesome in return for supporting my content❤️

Click on my profile to get access to these designs and so much more!🥰

#notalone #merchdesign #mentalhealthmatters #inspirationalquotes #adhd #neurodivergent

The worst part about ADHD is the generation of people we have bred that don’t believe in themselves when they have these brains that can become GIFTS if used in the proper light.  If you know someone with ADHD please encourage their ideas….it will make their day more then you could ever believe❤️ #adhd #adhdsupport #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #adhdawareness

ADHD & Overwhelm can very much go hand in hand so IT’S UP TO US to create an environment as simple as possible especially when it’s not what we are use to❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdlife #adhdtips

ADHD & Low Dopamine can cause PROBLEMS considering that can be the lead cause for a lack of Concentration, Motivation, Pleasure, AND Emotional Regulation.  Many of us tend to overthink where Dopamine comes from so I wanted to make a video to remind you of the simplicity❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdbrain #adhdmemes #dopamine #adhdtips

Overthinking has to be one of the harder parts of ADHD because we always assume there is something WAY more complex but the fact is that if we treat our brain like its on purpose it can solve SO MANY lf the issues most ADHD’rs struggle with.  Keep it simple and keep going, YOU’RE WORTH IT #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdtips #adhdbrain #adhdsupport #adhdlife

ADHD and getting tired quickly is surprisingly common so here is a more simple explanation as to why it happens.  I hope it helps❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #adhdproblems #adhdsupport #adhdlife

You’re brain won’t rest…or you haven’t figured out how to make your brain rest yet.  I promise this answer is out there because there IS an answer so give yourself that empathy and get experimenting.  Here’s a few things that I know are known to help ❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdproblems #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdtips #adhdbrain

People with ADHD tend to love things that satisfy our brains for free much more then others….its an addictive tendancy of our brains and its hard to convince ourselves to not want those things especially when we need to do something that requires a lot more effort so here are some fun things i recognize so my brain still knows its going to have a good time❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdtips #adhdbrain

Impulsivity and ADHD unfortunately are EXTREMELY common especially for those with an untreated brain so to simplify things for yourself try living by the H.A.L.T method to help you identify if you are treating yourself kindly or not❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdproblems #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #adhdsupport #adhdtips

Caffeine is such a HUGE subject for people with ADHD and a very handy tool to help us in our tough days.  I feel that it gets so demonized by people even though i do recognize that the abuse is real so i hope this video explains why these things happen for us so we can appropriatly take advantage!❤️ #adhd #adhdbrain #adhdawareness #adhdtips #adhdmemes #adhdproblems #adhdlife

ADHD & Dating is SUCH a big subject and there are so many variables we are never told to consider but one thing that NEEDS to be talked about more is the role of Dopamine and how it plays in to our selection ESPECIALLY for those that are low in it!  I hope this video helps explain it a little more❤️ #adhd #adhdrelationships #adhdawareness #dopamine #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #adhdsupport
No matter the mask you wear today i just wanted to repost this video to remind you that you are worth being here❤️ #adhd #adhdsupport #adhdawareness #adhdlife
You ok?  There’s help closer then you think.  #mentalhealthawareness #adhd

Getting accomodations for ADHD can be tricky especially because the research that ACTUALLY helps us is so brand new and you will need to find a company who is horrendously on top of this😅. My best advice for the world we live in is to understand yourself before asking others so then you will know how to direct them to an appropriate accomadation.  Youve got this❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdaccommodations #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #adhdtips

Invalidating what and ADHD’er should be focusing on is so popular and it’s so silly because these simple holistic values can mean so much to a brain that needs a little more of a manual push.  Please don’t let these people get to you,  understand that they don’t know any better, and keep working on yourself.  There are answers out there that are worth finding out!❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdlife #adhdsupport

The treated vs untreated state happens to us on a DAILY basis!  In some ways it’s so cool that our brain doesn’t let us get away with things but in other ways it can be intimidating!  This is why it’s so good to have people on your side that know how to help which is why we should value an ADHD care platform such as @doneadhd give them a shot in the link in my bio and see if they are the right fit for you! #adhd #adhdbrain #adhdsupport #adhdtips

ADHD people talk themselves out of tasks a little too quickly sometimes and one of the most common is TAKING CARE OF THE ADHD BRAIN!  This is a hurtle worth hurtling because it makes the rest of our day so much more tolerable so i wanted to share this message❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdproblems #adhdsupport #adhdbrain

ADHD & Praise is an interesting subject because we never want to over value someone but interestingly for a rejection sensitive brain we tend to develop the feeling that an over value means value and with a mind that prioritizes what is currently being thought about it certainly doesnt hurt to have such a good reminder❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdbrain

ADHD & Stimming comes in many forms but one of my favourites that doesn’t get talked about enough is the excitement stim!  These can be done Vocally, Physically, or by Simple movements…simply put i like to say that it’s just us getting goofy!  I hope you enjoy🥰❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdlife #adhdbrain

Drinking water is stressed about for ANYONE with Mental Health issues because it’s SO. BLOODY. GOOD FOR YOU and ADHD is no exception!  As an educator in this space my first question to all clients is “How is your water intake and do you know why that is important?” So i made this video to help explain!❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdtips #adhdbrain

I got very emotional making this video.  People can call content creation whatever they want but way too many people use it to sell a T-shirt or to sell a program when they can be using it to bring awareness to the world of Mental Health and incredible resources such as @whiteflagapp that gives people an anonymous way to get help and this freaking app should be on EVERYONE IN THE WORLDS phone with no exception.  If you’re like me and you are tired of paying for a company to disappoint you then help me bring awareness to this unbelievable company that is doing everything for free. #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdsupport

ADHD & Praise can go very far for a rejection sensitive neurochemically deficient brain because knowing how good it can feel can send us in to a pursuit of wanting that praise again & again and setting up a CONSENSUAL ENVIRONMENT  where that praise is attainable is something that most neurodiverse people can feel incredibly comfortable around which can only enhance our experiences🖤 #adhdafterdark #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #kinkcommunity #kinkmemes

Establishing weekly routines can be TOUGH for those with a spontaneous brain so after tons of attempts at different methhods to help me i found this to be this BEST way to start a scattered day!  It just helps get the direction of the day going so i hope it helps❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdtips #adhdbrain #adhdsupport

Dopamine can be rewarded from a truly insane amount of ways and its hard to fully understand but the one thing we know perfectly is that our mind fixates on what is creating our Motivational Neurotransmitter and tends to push off things that don’t make it nearly as well.  Flirting can be a dangerous one that leads a lot of us down a rough rabbit hole so I hope this helps explain things❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #adhdsupport #adhdrelationships #dopamine

My RSD absolutely triggers when I talk about myself life this but I think a pinned video for my page is helpful.
I have over 1000 videos and no one knows how to find the categories so this is my attempt to work on myself a bit more to help keep organized FOR YOU!!

My account will now be dedicated to these 5 categories of short form content.  There will also be 🌶️ content available for detailed 18+ education on another platform and long form content through YouTube that will answer so many of the follow up questions on my videos all in one place such is “How” “Why” “Where to start” and “Do you wear makeup?!”

I hope that you guys enjoy my content because I love making it for you!🥰
#adhd #adhdawareness #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #adhdbrain #adhdtips

Do you ever think back to a smile?

What made me do that?  Why was I willing?  Why aren’t I doing that right now?  Was it real?

The crazy part is that could have been the second I finished a good energy drink… I could have just watched an inappropriate comedy special, I could have eaten a big ol’ breakfast….Christ….it could have even been that I just felt like it and yet…

At this very moment a smile seems like it needs to be something special, like it needs to be deserved, or like it has to mean something.

Sometimes we forget that our brain plays in to what we give it…..almost as if we are in control of this thing wether we are in a good mood or a bad mood.

Please don’t ever forget that your smile has the ability to both light up the world and hide the world from what you don’t want them to know.

The crazy part is….it’s up to you to determine the meaning….no matter how simple or complex.

I….I lost the point of this post.  Here’s a pic of me smiling.  Determine the story for yourself🤪

Its not easy for us to accept but there are absolutely some disclaimers that come with the ADHD brain….the interesting thing to understand though is that when those disclaimers are understood then a relationship can really thrive and both parties can share a wonderful love!  Its when they are hidden that things can become difficult so I hope this helps❤️ #adhd #adhdrelationships #adhdawareness #adhdbrain #adhdtips #adhdmemes

A submissive mind goes hand in hand with the opposites of the stress associated with a scattered brain and it becomes such a wonderful release when we find the right person to give us this freedom so i hope this video makes you smile and gets you in a mood😈❤️ #adhd #adhdafterdark #adhdmemes #adhdlife #adhdbrain #adhdawareness

Alcohol Addiction mixed with an ADHD brain is WAY TOO COMMON!!!! There are a million more points that i wanted to make but i can only say so much in a minute.  Please make good choices in your life.  There are so freaking many forms of stimulation and while this is one of them…it’s not the only one.  You matter,  you’ve got this❤️ #adhd #addiction #alcohol #adhdawareness #adhdmemes #adhdproblems #adhdbrain

Medication is SUCH a big subject in the ADHD world and the one very scary topic to discuss is “do I only stay busy when my pills are in my system because that’s when I can focus” so I hope this addresses that a bit and helps you understand❤️ #adhd #adhdmedication #adhdparenting #adhdawareness #adhdbrain #adhdtips

Impulsivity can lead people with ADHD down some BAD rabbit holes and it’s important to understand that there are ways to help.  I figure all of you have heard “Make a planner” a million times so heres some different ones that work for me!❤️ #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdsupport #adhdlife #adhdmemes #adhdtips #adhdadult

Parents create the primary judgement that a child feels pressure from in their lives.  I was so different from my parents and i was absolutely led to believe that i was born a “problem child” when in reality the is the laziest and most out of touch thing a parent can ever lay in to their child. “Take the easy way out” “Those kids are making fun of your weirdness because they aren’t good friends” give me a break.  Im sharing this to hopefully hit one family in a positive light.  Get to know yourselves, it can make all the difference❤️ #adhd #adhdparenting #neurodivergent #adhdbrain #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdlife

ADHD & Serious relationships are a tricky structure.  We have a brain that when its not taken care of it can really punish us so to find someone willing to be there for all the positives and the negatives can be hard ESPECIALLY when we aren’t truthful with them or ourselves.  If we understand/accept that we have a brain that needs attention and portray that on to our partner it can change everything so I hope this video helps make that clear❤️ #adhd #adhdrelationships #adhdproblems #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdlife #adhdbrain

120,000 Users, over 1 million messages of support, and totally free for you from a company literally trying to lead the movement in #mentalhealthmatters💚 please give them your time.  Social Media has a power to launch a company so far and this. Is. The. Company.  Let’s help them help the world❤️ #adhd #neurodivergent #adhdmemes #depression #lgbtq #racism

ADHD & Bratty behaviour from an After Dark standpoint BLOWS MY MIND at how much it correlates and makes so much sense why it seems to be so common on our wonderful side of the internet so here is 1 of 137 ways i can deacribe the bratty nature of an After Dark loving ADHD’er😈❤️ #adhd #adhdafterdark #adhdwomen #adhdmen #adhdmemes #kinkcommunity #kinkmemes #booktok

Parenting. Is. SCARY!  Especially for the ADHD parents right now because its just a bad idea to look to your elders or even your primary peers for advice.  Your children have a DIFFERENT brain but a very interesting one with unique skills and if you take the time to understand them more you are going to unlock things in those children that most of us adults literally don’t have the ability to develop!  Please keep your faith high and learn about your child…..they don’t know it yet but they will be so thankful for you doing that one day❤️ #adhd #adhdparenting #adhdbrain #adhdtips #adhdsupport

IT ALL MAKES SENSE DOESN’T IT?! How many boring books did you not remember? How many snooze worthy classes did you struggle with in school? How many times did bad teachers not teach you anything?! I hope this really opens your mind because when we find a way to stimulate we find a way to unlock our true potential!! #adhd #adhdmemes #adhdawareness #adhdtips

LET’S ACTUALLY DO THIS!  I know i will get 1 on 1 time with these people and we need to get these questions to them!  They will have full access to my account to answer as many questions as they would like!  Get detailed…..these are the people to ask❤️ #adhd #adhdbrain #adhdawareness #adhdtips

I’m sick to my stomach posting this.  I shouldn’t have drank, i shouldn’t have been so blind because there were absolutely signs, and in a big way i don’t feel like it’s appropriate to talk about but I think any awareness around this is a good idea.  If your friend tells you something like this happens please double check with them if they are ok…..I wasn’t and noone did.  Thank you for listening.  #mentalhealthawareness #saawareness #adhd #mensmentalhealth #sad

The ADHD brain CAN be under control….don’t let anyone tell you that it can’t.  The beauty of our brain is that when we put in the work we unlock a brain that his LITERAL abilities other brains dont have but when we treat it badly we unlock curses that they don’t have….the choice and the journey are in our control so PLEASE take this seriously and recognize that you have a chance❤️ #adhd #adhdmemes #adhdsupport #adhdbrain #adhdawareness

Getting an ADHD disgnosis might unlock the one door you never knew was available and it could your life!  Dont discount it just because of the intrusive “who needs medication” talk!  Inquire about your brain,  you only get one!!! #adhd #adhdawareness #adhdproblems #adhdsupport
